text: Woman of the Year is a 1942 American romantic comedy movie directed by George Stevens and starring Spencer Tracy, Katherine Hepburn, Fay Bainter, Reginald Owen, William Bendix, Gladys Blake, Roscoe Karns. It was distributed by Metro- Goldwyn-Mayer and was nominated for 2 Oscars and won an Academy Award in 1943. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1942 romantic comedy movies Category:MGM movies Category:American romantic comedy movies Category:Movies directed by George Stevens
